            <title>[SPARK-53288] Fix assertion error when using StreamingGlobalLimit and Checkpoint v2</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-53288</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Checkpoint V2 has an assertion:&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;{{assert(      ret.length == getStateInfo.numPartitions,&lt;br/&gt;
      s&quot;ChekpointInfo length: ${ret.length}, numPartitions: ${getStateInfo.numPartitions}&quot;)}}&lt;br/&gt;
But StreamingGlobalLimit has only one partition.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix should be just relaxing this check for operators that have only 1 partition.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
